									<ul>
										<li>PrestaShop 1.6 to 8.x</li>
										<li>PrestaShop 1.7 to 8.x</li>
										<li>Minor version updates</li>
										<li>Security patches</li>
										<li>Module compatibility</li>
									</ul>
								</div>
								<div class="migration-card">
									<div class="migration-icon">üè†</div>
									<h4>Hosting Migration</h4>
									<p>Move your PrestaShop store to a new hosting provider</p>
									<ul>
										<li>Server-to-server migration</li>
