									</ul>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="migration-process">
							<h3>Our Migration Process</h3>
							<div class="process-steps">
								<div class="step">
									<div class="step-number">1</div>
									<div class="step-content">
										<h4>Pre-Migration Analysis</h4>
										<p>Comprehensive audit of your current store, data structure, and custom modifications to plan the perfect migration strategy.</p>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="step">
									<div class="step-number">2</div>
									<div class="step-content">
										<h4>Backup & Preparation</h4>
										<p>Complete backup of all data, files, and configurations. Setup of staging environment for testing.</p>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="step">
									<div class="step-number">3</div>
									<div class="step-content">
										<h4>Data Migration</h4>
										<p>Careful migration of products, customers, orders, and all associated data with integrity checks.</p>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="step">
									<div class="step-number">4</div>
									<div class="step-content">
										<h4>Testing & Validation</h4>
										<p>Thorough testing of all functionality, data integrity verification, and performance optimization.</p>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="step">
									<div class="step-number">5</div>
									<div class="step-content">
										<h4>Go-Live & Support</h4>
										<p>Seamless switch to the new system with minimal downtime and post-migration support.</p>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="guarantees">
							<h3>Our Migration Guarantees</h3>
							<div class="guarantees-grid">
								<div class="guarantee-item">
									<div class="guarantee-icon">üõ°Ô∏è</div>
									<h4>Zero Data Loss</h4>
									<p>Complete data preservation with multiple backup layers and integrity verification.</p>
								</div>
								<div class="guarantee-item">
									<div class="guarantee-icon">‚è±Ô∏è</div>
									<h4>Minimal Downtime</h4>
									<p>Strategic migration timing to minimize impact on your business operations.</p>
								</div>
								<div class="guarantee-item">
									<div class="guarantee-icon">üîç</div>
									<h4>SEO Preservation</h4>
									<p>Maintain your search engine rankings with proper URL redirects and SEO structure.</p>
								</div>
								<div class="guarantee-item">
									<div class="guarantee-icon">üéØ</div>
									<h4>Functionality Testing</h4>
									<p>Comprehensive testing to ensure all features work perfectly after migration.</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="sidebar">
						<div class="migration-checklist">
							<h4>Migration Checklist</h4>
							<ul class="checklist">
								<li>‚úÖ Products & Categories</li>
								<li>‚úÖ Customer Data</li>
								<li>‚úÖ Order History</li>
								<li>‚úÖ Payment Methods</li>
								<li>‚úÖ Shipping Settings</li>
								<li>‚úÖ Tax Configuration</li>
								<li>‚úÖ Custom Modules</li>
								<li>‚úÖ Theme & Design</li>
								<li>‚úÖ SEO Settings</li>
								<li>‚úÖ Analytics Setup</li>
							</ul>
						</div>

						<div class="pricing-card">
							<h4>Migration Pricing</h4>
							<div class="price-item">
								<span class="price-label">Platform Migration</span>
								<span class="price-value">From $1,999</span>
							</div>
							<div class="price-item">
								<span class="price-label">Version Upgrade</span>
								<span class="price-value">From $799</span>
							</div>
							<div class="price-item">
								<span class="price-label">Hosting Migration</span>
								<span class="price-value">From $499</span>
							</div>
							<p class="pricing-note">*Pricing depends on store complexity and data volume</p>
							<a href="/#contact" class="primary-button">Get Quote</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="contact-cta">
			<div class="container">
				<h2>Ready to Migrate or Upgrade Your Store?</h2>
				<p>Get a free migration assessment and detailed project plan from our experts</p>
				<a href="/#contact" class="primary-button">Start Migration Project</a>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
	<Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
	.service-hero {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f1f3c 0%, #2c5aa0 100%);
		color: white;
		padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
		margin-top: 80px;
	}

	.breadcrumb {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		opacity: 0.8;
	}

	.breadcrumb a {
		color: white;
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.breadcrumb a:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}

	.service-hero h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.hero-subtitle {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		opacity: 0.9;
		max-width: 600px;
	}

	.content-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	.service-overview {
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.service-overview h2 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		color: #0f1f3c;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.service-overview p {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		color: #4b5563;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.migration-types {
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.migration-types h3 {
		font-size: 1.75rem;
		color: #0f1f3c;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.migration-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.migration-card {
		background: white;
		border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
		border-radius: 16px;
		padding: 2rem;
		text-align: center;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.migration-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-4px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}

	.migration-icon {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.migration-card h4 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #0f1f3c;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.migration-card p {
		color: #6b7280;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.migration-card ul {
		list-style: none;
		text-align: left;
	}

	.migration-card li {
		padding: 0.25rem 0;
		color: #4b5563;
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		position: relative;
		padding-left: 1rem;
	}

	.migration-card li::before {
		content: '‚Ä¢';
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: #2c5aa0;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.migration-process {
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.migration-process h3 {
		font-size: 1.75rem;
		color: #0f1f3c;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.process-steps {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.step {
		display: flex;
		gap: 2rem;
		align-items: flex-start;
	}

	.step-number {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c5aa0, #1e40af);
		color: white;
		width: 50px;
		height: 50px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		font-weight: 600;
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.step-content h4 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #0f1f3c;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.step-content p {
		color: #6b7280;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.guarantees h3 {
		font-size: 1.75rem;
		color: #0f1f3c;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.guarantees-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.guarantee-item {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		align-items: flex-start;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background: #f8fafc;
		border-radius: 12px;
	}

	.guarantee-icon {
		font-size: 2rem;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.guarantee-item h4 {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #0f1f3c;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.guarantee-item p {
		color: #6b7280;
		line-height: 1.6;
		font-size: 0.875rem;
	}

	.sidebar {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.migration-checklist {
		background: #f8fafc;
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 16px;
	}

	.migration-checklist h4 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: #0f1f3c;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.checklist {
		list-style: none;
	}

	.checklist li {
		padding: 0.5rem 0;
		color: #4b5563;
		font-size: 0.875rem;
	}

	.pricing-card {
		background: white;
		border: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
		border-radius: 16px;
		padding: 2rem;
	}

	.pricing-card h4 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: #0f1f3c;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.price-item {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 1rem 0;
		border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
	}

	.price-item:last-of-type {
		border-bottom: none;
	}

	.price-label {
		color: #4b5563;
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.price-value {
		color: #2c5aa0;
		font-weight: 600;
		font-size: 1.125rem;
	}

	.pricing-note {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		color: #6b7280;
		text-align: center;
		margin: 1rem 0;
		font-style: italic;
	}

	.contact-cta {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc, #e2e8f0);
		padding: 4rem 0;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.contact-cta h2 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		color: #0f1f3c;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.contact-cta p {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		color: #6b7280;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.primary-button {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c5aa0, #1e40af);
		color: white;
		padding: 1rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 600;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(44, 90, 160, 0.3);
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		display: inline-block;
		width: 100%;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.primary-button:hover {
		transform: translateY(-3px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(44, 90, 160, 0.4);
	}

	@media (max-width: 968px) {
		.content-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.migration-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.guarantees-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.service-hero h1 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}
	}
</style>